<emphasis id="B93A3657FFC09E1E81C222B7382D4AC5" bold="true" box="[136,349,913,940]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="73">Curtia verticillaris</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFDF97B4FFC09E1E802922B73B124AC4" author="Knoblauch, E. F." box="[355,610,914,941]" pageId="12" pageNumber="73" pagination="323 - 357" refId="ref15849" refString="Knoblauch, E. F. (1894) Beitragezur Kenntniss der Gentianaceaea. Botanisches Centralblatt 60: 323 - 357." type="journal article" year="1894">Knoblauch (1894:357)</bibRefCitation>
